<br>
I cant even begin to count how many times i almost quit playing before 55, because being a wizard was not only a shitty job but you actually worsened a groups potential DPS moreso then any other class.<br>
<br>
Those problems are still there though at least you dont have to stare at a spell book anymore, but being that the only way a wizard can do damage is through there mana pool, and if you are untwinked that means 1, maybe 2 nukes per mob, with a snare/root every few mobs, if you want to maintain a constant damage rate.  Otherwise you can burn 1 down hard, then spend 15 mins regening mana, with regular clarity.<br>
<br>
Remember wizards are the weakest class sub 49 and were designed this way intentionally.<br>
<br>
You might not agree with him going to get a KEI, but I can garentee any wizard who has played for more then 2 years will certianly sympathise with him, as we have all known the utter crap that had to be endured, hours hunting for a group that would take a wizard.<br>
<br>
